## ğŸ¯ Why This Project Exists

In many schools, STEM students are required to write deep literary analysis, historical narratives, and reflective essays â€” in a foreign language, with no structured logic, under strict "no AI" rules.  
This project is a counterbalance.

We believe:
- AI tools don't destroy education â€” they **recover your time** and **extend your limits**.
- Using AI to clarify, summarize, and translate is not cheating â€” it's **accessibility**.
- Writing with AI **doesn't mean giving up thinking** â€” it means **thinking more clearly**.

